title: FARA Communications (Department of Justice, Executive Office for United States Attorneys)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

all FARA communications between Executive Office for United States Attorneys and NDS regarding or citing Hunter Biden or Jim Biden and 611(k) or 611k or 611 (k) or 611 k between January 1, 2000 and December 15, 2022.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

TheWinger

title: FBI Investigation of Seattle demonstrations in 2020-2021 by Special Agent Raymond Duda

communications.subject: Freedom of Information Act Request: FBI Investigation of Seattle demonstrations in 2020-2021 by Special Agent Raymond Duda
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Please provide investigative documents from Special Agent Raymond Duda on Black Lives Matter demonstrations in Seattle during 2020-2021.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Daniel Stiggler
